flowchart LR
    CP["CP / Packet 配置"] --> Glb["GlbCtrl<br/>接收 kernel packet / reg info"]
    Glb --> LC["kernel -> logic cluster"]
    LC --> PC["选择 physical cluster"]
    PC --> Clus["目标 physical cluster 的 ClusCtrl"]
    Clus --> B["logic cluster -> block"]
    B --> Core["Core 执行 block"]
    Core --> ClusAck["block release / response"]
    ClusAck --> GlbAck["cluster ack / response"]
    GlbAck --> Done["kernel_done 给 CP"]
